  - Rect → `<rect>` with `x`, `y`, `width`, `height`, `fill`, `stroke`.
  - Text → `<text>` with `x`, `y`, `font-family`, `font-size`, `fill`.
  - Lines/paths → `<path>` or `<line>` with `stroke`, `stroke-dasharray` for dotted.
